Parent Detector
Laser Trip detection system with LDR, Piezo-Buzzer and Camera using Raspberry Pi.

ICARUS Report Card Server
Report card management system using Python, MySQL and Tkinter.
Teachers can login using the master password to set up student report cards and view,

Students can login using their credentials to view their report card and change their
login password.
PixCrypt Image Encryptor
Two-level Base64 + AES image encryption using Python, PyCryptodome and
CustomTkinter.
Users can encrypt images with a password of their choice and send them via email or
save it locally.
Level of encryption is based on the batch size (128/192/256 bit).
The receiver can decrypt the images by using the same password.
Laundry Logger

Simple and small-sized device to enable students to keep track of their laundry count.
One button for incrementing the count and another button for resetting. The count is
displayed using dual 7-segment displays.
